{
  "texts": [
    "Other chains were not considered during analysis.",
    "For every residue that was labelled as binding, points within 4.5Å of the residue were saved.",
    "Points that were saved three or more times (i.e.",
    "were within 4.5Å of three or more residues labelled as binding) were clustered using the DBSCAN algorithm from Scikit-learn [61], using a 1.7Å cutoff to separate clusters.",
    "Clusters were ranked simplistically, using the total number of points in the cluster (including repetitions of the same point), and the centres of the top-ranked clusters were calculated by taking the mean coordinates of all points."
  ]
}